@startuml UC_ViewApps
skinparam conditionStyle diamond
skinparam nodesep 100
skinparam ranksep 60
title Activity: View Applicants
|Employer|
start
:Select Job Post;
|System|
:Fetch Applicants List;
:Display Applicants;
|Employer|
:Filter (Status, Match Score);
repeat
  :Select Applicant;
  |System|
  :Fetch Applicant Profile/Resume;
  :Display Details;
  |Employer|
  :Review Resume & Profile;
  fork
    -> Keep Pending;
  fork again
    -> Shortlist;
    :Click Shortlist;
    |System|
    :Update Status to Shortlisted;
  fork again
    -> Reject;
    :Click Reject;
    |System|
    :Update Status to Rejected;
    :Send Rejection Email (Optional);
  end fork
|Employer|
repeat while (More Applicants?) is (yes)
-> no;
stop
@enduml
